==English==

===Noun===
'''emergence'''
# The act of [[rise|rising]] out of a [[fluid]], or coming forth from [[envelopment]] or [[concealment]], or of rising into view; sudden [[uprisal]] or [[appearance]].
# In particular: the arising of [[emergent]] structure in complex systems.

